description:
This is a 10 minute workout called 'Daily Calm | 10 Minute Mindfulness Meditation | Forgetting Time' from the channel Calm.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Tamara Levitt guides this 10 minute Daily Calm mindfulness meditation. Enjoy an experiential practice that explores the importance of forgetting time....
